00:04:32.270 --> 00:04:36.280
then we take the dashed line,
basically going to the bottom,

80
00:04:36.280 --> 00:04:42.990
finding on the x-axis the price
that generates this revenue.

81
00:04:42.990 --> 00:04:47.130
And this is the price we're
saying is gonna maximize revenue,

82
00:04:47.130 --> 00:04:50.068
in this case $5.50.

83
00:04:50.068 --> 00:04:54.520
