to do something with the quantity.

88
00:05:05.770 --> 00:05:09.220
It has actions the company or
the consumer can take.

89
00:05:09.220 --> 00:05:12.176
It can be changing the price,
producing product,

90
00:05:12.176 --> 00:05:16.460
